description: Try our easy to follow Pumpkin & Pasta Soup recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Soup,Low saturated fat,High fibre,High protein,Seafood free,Tree nut free,Low sugar,Low fat,Sesame free,Peanut free
name: Pumpkin & Pasta Soup Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Place soup and 3/4 cup water in a saucepan over medium-high heat, then bring to the boil. Add pasta, then reduce heat to medium-low and simmer, stirring occasionally, for 10 minutes or until pasta is tender and mixture thickens.
Heat a frying pan over medium-high heat. Cook wraps for 2 minutes on each side or until beginning to char.
Ladle soup among bowls. Season well with salt and pepper. Serve with wraps.
